skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sounds of waterfall
des:
Fall into a deep sleep with our dreamy waterfall sounds. Sounds of Waterfall is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. 

All you need to do is say Alexa start Sounds of Waterfall, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
